title: Beatnik Charades
description:
Written by Alene Latimer
Starring: Dan Hodapp, Kelly Hudson, Lisa Kleinman, Avery Monsen

Directed by Jim Santangeli

From Maude Night at the Upright Citizens Brigade Theatre, Feb. 4, 2013.

Filmed by Tom Levin, Curtis Raye.
Edited by Curtis Raye.
